# >>> council-internal transient artifacts >>>
# Per-run scratch state + workspace-level sentinels — never committed.
# All transient council artifacts (contributions/, .session-state.json,
# .adjourn-snapshot.json, .lifecycle-complete, .route-log, .preserve-runs,
# .production-mode, .reevaluation-marker, .inbox/) live under .council/.
# Forensic council artifacts under docs/council/ (report.md,
# execution-log.md, deliberations/, INDEX.md, research/, members/) ARE
# committed via build's selective git-add (build/SKILL.md SBdX3).
# This block is plugin-managed: do not add custom council entries here
# OR elsewhere in .gitignore; the manage-gitignore.sh script strips any
# orphan .council or docs/council pattern on every adjourn entry.
.council/
